                 AoA Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) Page
                         and Electronic Reading Room
   _____________________________________________________________________

   Welcome to the AoA FOIA Home Page. We hope you will find this site
   informative and that it will facilitate your efforts to obtain public
   information about AoA programs. We will continue to provide you with
   more current program information as more electronic information becomes
   available.

   Freedom of Information Act (FOIA) as amended by Public Law 104-231 (HHS
   Web Site)

   Guide to Information Resources (including How to Request FOIA
   Information)
   _____________________________________________________________________

  Electronic Reading Room:  Major AoA Official Documents and Other Information

     * Program Instructions issued by AoA to the State and Area Agencies
       on Aging starting in FY 1997
     * Information Memoranda  issued by AoA to the State and Area Agencies
       on Aging starting in FY 1997
     * AoA Program Announcements:  FY2001; FY2000;  FY1999; FY1998
     * AoA Press Releases
     * National Aging Information Center
     * National Aging Program Information System (NAPIS):
          + State Program Reports (SPR)
          + National LTC Ombudsman Reporting System (NORS)

   For additional information resources, see the Site Index for the AoA
   Web Site.
